Here's the reply to Dcoburn's post. It may come in a second time 
later, but its better than not coming in at all.

::Zardus/Oblitertron::

Oblitertron growls at Dark Lavatron, raising his weapon, about to 
open fire. Out of the corner of his eyes, he sees Zardus motioning 
for him to back off. Reluctantly, Dark One takes a step back, 
watching Zardus fly forward.

Oblitertron had been looking forward to killing these puny bots, 
maybe battle would still be possible....
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus looks at Lavatron, thinking the offer over. Bots like these 
could be an asset, yesss...

"What kind of alliance do you have in mind?" Zardus asks mindly, his 
weapon ready just in case, "You joining us?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
